two weeks from "Baking Chez

00:38:44.180 --> 00:38:47.700
Moi" and the other two weeks
from "Baking with Julia."

00:38:47.700 --> 00:38:49.920
And so anybody
who wants to start

00:38:49.920 --> 00:38:54.690
baking with this group of
fabulous, supportive, generous,

00:38:54.690 --> 00:38:57.770
adorable people, it's
Tuesday with Dorie--

00:38:57.770 --> 00:39:02.820
you have to Google
it because I think

00:39:02.820 --> 00:39:04.742
it's like blogspot or something.

00:39:04.742 --> 00:39:06.200
It's got another
little word in it,

00:39:06.200 --> 00:39:09.684
but if you Google
Tuesdays with Dorie,

00:39:09.684 --> 00:39:11.350
the first thing you'll
get is some woman

00:39:11.350 --> 00:39:14.850
named Dorie who's not me who
